OL,3,CCost of sending a letter in Guernsey
OL,4,Cto increase
OL,6,FPeople in Guernsey will soon have to
OL,7,Fspend a little extra to post standard
OL,8,Fletters locally and to the UK.
OL,10,FGuernsey Post has announced tariff
OL,11,Fchanges that will take effect from 1
OL,12,FApril 2025.
OL,14,FThe local letter rate will increase
OL,15,Ffrom 65p to 69p, with the price of a
OL,16,FUK standard letter rising from #1.20
OL,17,Fto #1.37.
OL,19,FIt follows Jersey Post which also
OL,20,Fhiked its prices in January to cover
OL,21,Fhigher running costs.
